---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import FAQSchema from '../../components/FAQSchema.astro';
import { serviceFAQs } from '../../data/serviceFAQs';

const faqs = serviceFAQs['toner'];
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Toner" 
  price="Contact for pricing" 
  duration="30-45 minutes"
  image="/images/optimized/melissa-professional_800.webp"
>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Perfect Your Shade with Professional Toning</h2>
  
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Toner is the secret weapon for achieving your perfect hair color. This essential service neutralizes unwanted tones, enhances your existing color, and adds gorgeous shine. Whether you're maintaining your blonde, refreshing your brunette, or correcting brassy tones, our professional toning service delivers the polished finish your hair deserves.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What is Hair Toner?</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Hair toner is a semi-permanent color treatment that deposits pigment onto the hair shaft without lifting your natural color. It works by neutralizing unwanted undertones – think of it as a color corrector for your hair. Toners can cool down warm tones, add warmth to ashy shades, or simply refresh your existing color between major services.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Benefits of Professional Toning</h3>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li>Eliminates brassy and yellow tones</li>
    <li>Creates cooler, more refined blonde shades</li>
    <li>Adds incredible shine and glossy finish</li>
    <li>Refreshes faded color between appointments</li>
    <li>Customizable to achieve exact desired shade</li>
    <li>Gentle formula that conditions while coloring</li>
    <li>Quick service with immediate results</li>
    <li>Extends the life of your color investment</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Who Needs Toning?</h3>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Highlighted Hair</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Essential after lightening to achieve desired tone</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Brassy Blondes</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Neutralizes unwanted warm tones</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Faded Color</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Refreshes color between major services</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Gray Hair</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Eliminates yellow tones in silver hair</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Toner Color Guide</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Understanding toner shades helps achieve your perfect result:
  </p>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li><strong>Violet/Purple:</strong> Neutralizes yellow tones for cooler blondes</li>
    <li><strong>Blue:</strong> Cancels orange tones in brunettes and darker blondes</li>
    <li><strong>Green:</strong> Neutralizes red tones</li>
    <li><strong>Pearl/Silver:</strong> Creates icy, platinum effects</li>
    <li><strong>Beige/Sand:</strong> Adds warmth while maintaining neutral tone</li>
    <li><strong>Clear:</strong> Adds shine without changing color</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Toning Process</h3>
  <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li>Hair analysis to determine current tone</li>
    <li>Selection of appropriate toner shade</li>
    <li>Shampoo to prepare hair for even absorption</li>
    <li>Application of toner from roots to ends</li>
    <li>Processing time (typically 5-20 minutes)</li>
    <li>Monitoring for desired result</li>
    <li>Rinse with cool water to seal cuticle</li>
    <li>Conditioning treatment for added shine</li>
  </ol>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Toner vs. Purple Shampoo</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    While purple shampoo is great for maintenance, professional toning offers superior results:
  </p>
  <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Professional Toner</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>Customized formula</li>
          <li>Longer-lasting results</li>
          <li>Even application</li>
          <li>Multiple tone correction</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Purple Shampoo</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>General maintenance</li>
          <li>Temporary effect</li>
          <li>Can be patchy</li>
          <li>Limited to purple tones</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Maintaining Your Tone</h3>
  <div class="bg-[#FFDEE2] bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Make Your Toner Last:</h4>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Use color-safe, sulfate-free products</li>
      <li>Wash with cool water to prevent fading</li>
      <li>Limit washing to 2-3 times per week</li>
      <li>Use purple shampoo once weekly between toners</li>
      <li>Protect from sun and chlorine</li>
      <li>Schedule toner refresh every 3-4 weeks</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Perfect Finishing Touch</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Think of toner as the Instagram filter for your hair – it perfects and polishes your color to photogenic perfection. Melissa's expertise in color theory ensures your toner is perfectly customized to complement your skin tone and achieve your desired result, whether that's icy platinum, warm honey, or anything in between.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-[#D3E4FD] bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg p-6">
    <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
      "Toner is often the difference between good hair color and great hair color. It's that final step that takes your look from 'nice' to 'wow!' – and at such an affordable price, there's no reason not to have perfectly toned hair all the time."
    </p>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>

<!-- FAQ Schema -->
<FAQSchema 
  faqs={faqs} 
  pageUrl="https://hairbymelissa.co.nz/services/toner"
/>